# ADLC Evals Project Rules

## Package Manager
- This project uses **bun** as the package manager and runtime
- Use `bun install` instead of `npm install`
- Use `bun run` instead of `npm run`
- Use `bun add` instead of `npm install <package>`
- Use `bunx` instead of `npx`

## Project Structure
- `generated-report-sites/` - Next.js report sites for different platform comparisons
- `generated-reports/` - Markdown reports generated by AI agents
- `meta-research-prompts/` - Research prompts for report generation

## Next.js Sites
- Sites use Next.js 16+ with React 19
- Turbopack is enabled for dev (`bun run dev` uses `--turbopack`)
- Use TypeScript for all new code
- Tailwind CSS for styling
